Involved in multiple projects around Business Intelligence, Data Migration and Data warehousing that range from developing BI prototypes, end to end development, data migration, data transformation, datawarehouse maintenance and upgrades,  etc

•	Working as a Sole BI developer for PA2E project delivering Data Migration and Business Intelligence Solution using SSIS / SSAS and SSRS 2008
•	Working on Large Data Migration project to migrate data from different sources, transform and cleanse data and load into Ellipse ERP system
•	Cleansing, conversion, extraction, transformation, migration and loading of data into ERP system and into Data warehouse;
•	Developing optimised data integration processes for extracting, transforming and loading data from a variety of data sources into data warehouses;
•	Developing Stored Procedures and T-SQL Functions for ETL process
•	Create Drill Through reports and Parameterized reports using hyperlink actions, including Jump to URL and Jump to Report
•	Developing analytical reports (pivot tables and charts), parameterized reports, drill through reports and ad-hoc reporting models to meet business requirements within a BI solution;
•	Design, development & implementation of Analysis Services components in a Microsoft SQL Server Analysis Services (SSAS) including MDX;

Source Systems: Spreadmarts, MapInfo data (GIS), Ellipse, Hi Affinity, IFBIS and HRIS systems

